Final Results for Classification
As shown in , the final results on the movie review dataset are consistent with the development results , where S - LSTM outperforms BiL - STM significantly , with a faster speed .

among.from sentence: As shown in , among the 16 datasets of , S - LSTM gives the best results on 12 , compared with BiLSTM and 2 layered BiL - STM models .

of.from sentence: The average accuracy of S - LSTM is 85.6 % , significantly higher compared with 84.9 % by 2 - layer stacked BiLSTM .

Final Results for Sequence Labelling
For NER , S - LSTM gives an F1 - score of 91.57 % on the CoNLL test set , which is significantly better compared with BiLSTMs .
